    Results after Improvements v1: 
        Accuracy at 7.5% - 12.5%, barely above random guessing (5%)
        Training accuracy at ~95% - 100% -> Overfitting
        Causes: 
            Insufficient data -> 120 training samples for 20 classes
            Dropout of 50% not enough

