4 Class ANN:
    - 4 classes to represent the eletrodes, three electrodes were positioned on the middle finger, four on the hand, six on the forearm, and seven on the arm.
        Class 0 -> E1-E3 (Middle Finger)
        Class 1 -> E4-E7 (Hand)
        Class 2 -> E8-E13 (Forearm)
        Class 3 -> E14-E20 (Arm)

        Feature matrix shape: (160, 2187)
        Labels shape: (160,)
        Number of unique regions: 4
        Label distribution:
            Middle_Finger (Class 0): 24 samples
            Hand (Class 1): 32 samples
            Forearm (Class 2): 48 samples
            Arm (Class 3): 56 samples

